		"description":{
			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>As you shake off an enemy's control of your mind and body, you turn the tables by using its own power against it.</i></p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Daily</b></p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Immediate Interrupt</b><b> &#8226; </b><b>Special</b></p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Trigger:</b> You are subjected to an enemy's dazing, dominating, or stunning effect that a save can end. </p><p><b>Effect:</b> You make a saving throw against the effect. If your saving throw is successful, the triggering enemy must make a saving throw against the same effect. If that enemy's saving throw fails, the enemy is subjected to the effect (save ends). If your saving throw fails, you do not expend this power. </p><p>Published in Heroes of the Feywild, page(s) 27. </p>",
